00, and 16:00 UTC. The rate is determined by the premium/discount of the perpetual contract price relative to the spot index price over the funding interval. When the perpetual trades above spot (positive funding), long positions pay short positions, and vice versa. Bitget caps funding rates at ±2% per 8-hour period to prevent extreme scenarios."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
